Content summary part#1: To create a new spring boot project using Spring Initializr, one can go to start.spring.io. However, the app requires JavaScript to be enabled. The user can choose the project metadata, language, packaging, and dependencies. The app also provides options for generating and exploring the project, as well as sharing it.
